Interface TeamMember

    public interface TeamMember
    A team member represents something which has a meaningful Text representation on a Team. The client may be able to link the team Text entry to a particular object, and perform extra functionality.

    Examples include:

    • Players, represented in Vanilla by their name
    • Other living entities, represented in Vanilla by their UUID

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      Text getTeamRepresentation()
      Gets a Text representing this team member, suitable for adding to an Team with Team.addMember(Text).
